DevOps Interview Questions 

================================================
Questions covers the below tools/topics
================================================
GIT
Jenkins
Ansible
Dockers & Containers
Kubernetes
OpenShift
AWS
CI/CD
Scripting(Shell/Python)
Infra as a code (Terraform or Cloud Formation)
Linux (RHEL)
Monitoring (Application Monitoring, Log monitoring)


